  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nWe want to accept more attestations given clock disparity, however currently we narrow down the chance to get attestation at https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/13b61a32d2aa68177cc752918af57c24290f899f/packages/lodestar/src/chain/validation/attestation.ts#L176\r\n\r\nthis is due to this implementation\r\n```ts\r\nslotWithTolerance(toleranceSec: number): Slot {\r\n    return getCurrentSlot(this.config, this.genesisTime + toleranceSec);\r\n  }\r\n```\r\n\r\nwhich may lead to the confusion that it's the tolerance for the future but actually it's for the past\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n+ Implement `slotWithFutureTolerance` and `slotWithPastTolerance` api in clock to avoid the confusion",
